{"tid":921190,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)發夢王大歷險 翻生侏羅館1-3","createTime":"2018-11-29T10:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T17:44:58.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"64e3f303e95db92c5a29f518855f32ff098f06cc","tid":921190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:58:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=JMapTl%2F%2BfFbrePG30TsOpS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d577304c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=JMapTl%2F%2BfFbrePG30TsOpS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=43487dd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=JMapTl%2F%2BfFbrePG30TsOpS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=2e736648\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/c/cd/The_Secret_Life_of_Walter_Mitty_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fc%2Fcd%2FThe_Secret_Life_of_Walter_Mitty_poster.jpg&h=4f8458ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/07/Night_at_the_Museum_Secret_of_the_Tomb_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F07%2FNight_at_the_Museum_Secret_of_the_Tomb_poster.jpg&h=5bf1e956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.華特&bull;米堤（Walter Mitty）是一位《生活雜誌》的員工，但常常有各式各樣的白日夢。知名攝影師尚恩&bull;歐康諾（Sean O'Connell）有一天送了一捲特別的底片作品，並特別說明希望有一張相片能夠成為「生活雜誌」最後一期的封面。華特在底片影像部門工作，而過去十六年來從未弄丟過一張相片，然而這次卻找不到這張所謂的25號底片，因此從未真正出去冒險過的華特，決定出門尋找尚恩，找回失蹤的25號底片<br />\n<br />\n2.待業中的賴瑞終於找到工作，進入自然歷史博物館夜班守衛。本以為看守無人的博物館很輕鬆，想不到，一到晚上，展覽品不論人物動物都會復活，賴瑞除了要應付這群復活展品、躲避史前生物、更要搶救快被解體的博物館<br />\n<br />\n3.經營手電筒的賴瑞&middot;戴利（Larry Daley，班&middot;史提勒飾）事業有成後，收到「老朋友」牛仔傑迪戴亞（Jedediah，歐文&middot;威爾森飾）求救，再度回去博物館。原來首集的美國自然歷史博物館因應時代潮流，而把這批老舊展覽品，運送到世界最大的史密森尼博物館庫存，使得新博物館原有的展覽品也隨之全數復活。賴瑞得趕在破曉前，解決問題讓博物館回復原狀<br />\n<br />\n4.一隻考古隊誤打誤撞發現阿卡曼拉的陵墓，並且在不顧當地人「末日將至」的警告下強行取下黃金牌匾。 回到現代，賴瑞在博物館舉行一個盛大晚會，晚會前阿卡曼拉找到賴瑞，告訴賴瑞牌匾出了問題。賴瑞決定晚會結束後再來仔細檢視。晚會一開始十分順利，突然伴隨著牌匾的腐蝕，所有展品失控，人們紛紛逃出博物館，這次事件過後麥菲博士（館長）遭到撤職，賴瑞開始關注那塊牌匾，很快就找到當年發現牌匾時的記載，得知過去的夜班警衛-賽西也在當時陵墓挖掘的現場。隨後阿卡曼拉告訴賴瑞牌匾的秘密只有他父親-尼羅河法老知道，於是賴瑞讓麥菲博士將牌匾和阿卡曼拉轉移到大英博物館<br />\n<br />\n7 10PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=JMapTl%2F%2BfFbrePG30TsOpS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=30a67d40\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=JMapTl%2F%2BfFbrePG30TsOpS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=869f07fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34e2f7dd4ceff80695d0430b083663a58ac9483","tid":921190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9229f3f7ad0487385897db55b2d89d658c04064","tid":921190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1062d00faf4469c6e00adc537244e2178dad878","tid":921190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7ca4cfeab19d3793d520480d0d6a4a3bd5596a","tid":921190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eaa847131828ec029934e283b7fae19cc9c9141","tid":921190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3a575ac7865702f7526542b47004b5e9568324","tid":921190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011be35a3b024ea559cbc0d49faf0dc0809f5d02","tid":921190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as